Package: dvmisc
Type: Package
Title: Faster Computation of Common Statistics and Miscellaneous Functions
Version: 1.1.1
Date: 2017-11-03
Author: Dane R. Van Domelen
Maintainer: Dane R. Van Domelen <vandomed@gmail.com>
Description: Faster versions of base R functions (e.g. mean, standard deviation, covariance, and weighted mean) along with miscellaneous functions for various purposes (e.g. create histogram with fitted PDF/PMF curve, create BMI groups, assess linearity assumption in logistic regression, extract MSE from a fitted regression model).
LazyData: true
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), rbenchmark, microbenchmark
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.0), graphics, stats, MASS
LinkingTo: Rcpp
